't ask for blueberry or rainbow!                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Keren Carrion/NPR                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;"Before I knew the word feminism," Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg said in a 2014 interview, quoted in the cookbook, "seeing a sign for Russ &amp; Daughters taught me that women could matter just like men in an enterprise."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Since taking over the business, Niki Russ Federman and Josh Russ Tupper have added a bakery in Hudson Yards, a location in Brooklyn and a cafe, just a few blocks south of where their great-grandfather got his start.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;"We created this restaurant to have the sit-down appetizing experience," says Josh Russ Tupper. "Really, the way you should eat this is four-plus people. Get your platter of smoked fish. Order from the whole menu."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;On that menu: pickled herring trio, soft scrambled eggs with caviar, kasha varnishkas, borscht, and two kinds of babka French toast. One dish you won't find on that menu? Matzo brei.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;"It &lt;em&gt;was&lt;/em&gt;," explain Niki Russ Federman and Josh Russ Tupper.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-87357" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 9504;         --source-height: 6336;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1000/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1300/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1300w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2000/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 2000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 2600w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 1238px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 60px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 60px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1000/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1300/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1300w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2000/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 2000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg 2600w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 1238px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 60px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 60px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F48%2F81%2Fa9514ffa4ace8c6e8aa34f72840a%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-13.jpg" class="img" alt="Herring fish is a staple at Russ &amp;amp; Daughters." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Herring is a highlight of the shop, on its own or in a variety of salads.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Keren Carrion/NPR                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;"It seems simple," they write in their cookbook. "Sheets of matzo, soaked in water, then dipped in eggs and fried in butter."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;But it was driving everyone crazy.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;"Turns out that the simplest dish is the hardest," says Niki Russ Federman. "Matzo brei was the bane of our existence."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Everyone who ordered it, the cousins explain, had a memory from their childhood of &lt;em&gt;their&lt;/em&gt; matzo brei, or their grandmother's matzo brei, or their father's matzo brei. And they were all unhappy. "Because we could never match their taste memory," concludes Russ Federman.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-87330" class="bucketwrap image x-large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 9504;         --source-height: 6336;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1000/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 1000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1300/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 1300w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2000/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2Fca33a8664212957c85b6317cf0e4%2F20250826-russ-daughters-kc-27.jpg 2000w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/9504x6336+0+0/resize/2600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe9%2F21%2F