      <title>Amid debate about U.S. history, Harlem Hellfighters receive Congressional Gold Medal</title>
      <author>Alana Wise</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/09/06/g-s1-87313/amid-debate-about-u-s-history-harlem-hellfighters-receive-congressional-gold-medal</link>
