      <title>Concerned about federal vaccine policies, states are crafting their own</title>
      <author>Pien Huang</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2025/09/06/nx-s1-5532121/states-vaccine-guidance-washington-oregon-new-mexico</link>
